aa(lp246
VAs for the other drugs,
p247
aVlook at Portugal, where  nobody goes to jail
p248
aVfor possessing drugs,
p249
aVand the government's made  a serious commitment
p250
aVto treating addiction as a health issue.
p251
aVLook at Switzerland,  Germany, the Netherlands,
p252
aVDenmark, England, where people who have
p253
aVbeen addicted to heroin for many years
p254
aVand repeatedly tried to quit and failed
p255
aVcan get pharmaceutical  heroin and helping services
p256
aVin medical clinics, and  the results are in:
p257
aVIllegal drug abuse and disease
p258
aVand overdoses and crime  and arrests all go down,
p259
aVhealth and well-being improve,
p260
aVtaxpayers benefit,
p261
aVand many drug users even put their addictions behind them.
p262
aa(lp263
VLook at New Zealand, which  recently enacted a law
p264
aVallowing certain recreational  drugs to be sold legally
p265
aVprovided their safety had been established.
